headline: Communities, Police Nationwide Gather for National Night Out on August 5th to Promote Neighborhood Unity and Safety
summary: The National Association of Town Watch (NATW) invites citizens and law enforcement agencies across the country for National Night Out (NNO) on Tuesday, August 5, 2025, an annual community-building event that promotes police-community partnerships and neighborhood camaraderie.
